}}{{Metaphor.Alias
|Metaphor.Alias.Name=PURPOSEFUL ACTION IS GOAL-DIRECTED MOTION
}}
|Comments=This is a GENERIC IS SPECIFIC metaphor since the Self propelled purposeful motion frame incorporates the structure of the Purposeful action frame. 

In general, this metaphor assumes that the 'goal' location is in some sense more desirable than the 'source' location.
|Family=Location Event Structure Metaphor, LOVE IS A JOURNEY Cascade, Action is Motion metaphors, Primary Metaphors, 
|Metaphor Level=General
|Metaphor Type=Primary, Entailed
|Source frame=Self propelled motion to a destination
|Target frame=Purposeful action
|Mappings={{Mapping
|Target=objective
|Source=goal
|Comment=I.e. PURPSOSES ARE DESIRED LOCATIONS: goal has binding to objective in Source domain frame, and objective is bound to Desire.desired_situation
}}{{Mapping
|Target=actor
|Source=self-mover
|Comment=self-mover has binding to actor in Source domain frame
}}{{Mapping
|Target=action_x-schema
|Source=self-motion_x-schema
}}{{Mapping
|Target=action_x-schema_kind
|Source=path
|Comment=a.k.a., MEANS ARE PATHS
}}
